opennlp.ccg.perceptron
Class ReRankingPerceptronScorer

java.lang.Object
  opennlp.ccg.perceptron.PerceptronScorer
      opennlp.ccg.perceptron.ReRankingPerceptronScorer
All Implemented Interfaces:
ReRankingScorer, SignScorer
public abstract class ReRankingPerceptronScorer
extends PerceptronScorer
implements ReRankingScorer

A re-ranking sign scorer for a perceptron model. Note that at present, n-best re-ranking has been found to work better for parsing, but not for realization, where forest re-ranking (ie using the perceptron scorer throughout) seems to work better.
